|-
| Crush || [[File:SF6_icon_crush.png|x35px|class=sc-img-responsive]] || Appears when '''Drive Impact''' is '''blocked''' near the corner for a Wall Splat.
|-
| Lock || [[File:SF6_icon_lock.png|x35px|class=sc-img-responsive]] || Appears when '''Drive Impact''' connects against the opponent in a true blockstring. Cornered opponents will bounce off as though blocking a midscreen Drive Impact (no Wall Splat).
